Author: zombeezinthetrap
Text: Did I ghostwrited this post??? I’m experiencing a similar thing!! Pre-treatment I bought jeans that were my size but felt a little tight and used to leave marks on my skin. Now, post-treatment + relapse, the jeans fit comfortably. Yet, my brain thinks I’m fatter now because I’m not at my pre-treatment weight yet. 🤦🏿‍♀️
